	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Libentissime multis ad te scriberem, sed non possum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Hoc unum peto, ut, quacunque ratione possis, agas cum vicinis <placeName ref="l1107">Tridentino</placeName> concilio, ut, quid ibi fiat, explorent et diligenter ad te scribant, tu ad me.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de">Wie könnend die onmechtigen <placeName>Welschen</placeName> so fuul, unsorgsam und so untrüw sin!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="de">Tribend sy oder sagend, ir wöllind inen nüt me mitteylen.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Affini tuo dedi ultima, quae accepi, describenda tibi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Breviter: intelligo ex literis <persName ref="p540">Calvini</persName> rem esse in discrimine, eo quod <persName>Navarrenus</persName> parum sit firmus<note type="misc">Vgl. Die Wickiana, hg. v. <persName>Matthias Senn</persName>, 1975, S. 85 (Erwähnung der Mitteilung <persName ref="p540">Calvins</persName>)!</note>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">Sed dominus servabit nos et suam ecclesiam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Literas, quas paulo ante accepi, hic mitto, ne quid ignores et non habeas, quod ego habeo; sed ad proximum mercatum remitte haec.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Optime vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la">Plura essent scribenda; sed dixi: non possum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de">Drü bistumb, <placeName ref="l303">Magdenburg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1430">Hall</placeName> und <placeName ref="l1681">Merseburg</placeName> habend das bapstumb hingeworffen, ouch bischoff und thumcapittel; <foreign xml:lang="la">certissimum hoc.</foreign></s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de">Bischoff und capittel sind evangelisch worden, habend reformiert.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tiguri</placeName> 20. februarii 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la">Tuus, qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" ana="salute">Saluta, quos nosti, d. consules, <persName>Philippum</persName>, <persName ref="p6130">Pontisellam</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse S. 378:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro fideli, domino et fratri suo colendo et percharo.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l98">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
